This paper is about machine learning and specifically focuses on the sample complexity of learning linear predictors with the squared loss. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). Other likely sub-categories include cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.ST (Statistics), as these fields are closely related to machine learning. Additionally, since the paper deals with sample complexity, cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) and cs.IT (Information Theory) are also possible sub-categories.
